title: Not able to Quarkus native build
body:
### Describe the bug

We are trying to consume SOAP api from AWS quarkus lambda function. during the native build we are getting following error:"Provider com.sun.xml.internal.ws.spi.ProviderImpl not found".  Can anyone help here

### Expected behavior

native build should be completed without any error

### Actual behavior

We are getting following error at the time native build
error:"Provider com.sun.xml.internal.ws.spi.ProviderImpl not found"

### How to Reproduce?

Quarkus native build for SOA integration
